PWA GAP ANALYSIS - Technical Report¶

  • Created by Kevin Muhia Gathogo
  • Created on Jul 29, 2021
  • Runned on Mar 25, 2022 (feature.shape, Gives Current (x, y) x -total rows/features and y the current fields)

This is a gap analysis of ROADS_Asbuilt Dataset, EGIS SDE 64.

Roads_Asbuilts¶

Under Roads Asbuilt, we have three feature classes.

•   Carriageway
•   Road_Level
•   Road_Line

The report captures the total count of empty or null columns or unfilled attributes per each asset.

The unfilled attributes are highlighted in a summarised numerical count and visualised using bar graphs.
